title: The Wine Show S01E13 HDTV.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
The Wine Show - Series 1, Episode 13




From their villa HQ in the Italian hills, Matthew Goode and Matthew Rhys looks back at some of the highlights of the series. Joe Fattorini heads to South Africa for a taste of historic Vin de Constance. Matthew Rhys and Matthew Goode take us on a whistlestop tour of the 12 bottles that make up the Spirit of Italy case. Chef Francesco Mazzei travels to his home town of Calabria to enjoy another taste of his favourite wine. Amelia Singer goes to Australia to explore some of that country's greatest wines.




Original Air Date: 24-Jul-2016
